social_posts.post_text: HBD to the love of my life @aingelblood . So thankful that you entered my life. Coming up on 1 year of marriage, it’s been the best year I’ve had in a while. So excited for what’s next for you and for us!

Life Update: working on a solo album (first time I’m able to give it all my focus). Bout to get a degree. Moving out of Atlanta later this year. Just had my 1 year wedding anniversary. Still spooky to my core. Been working hard these past couple years tryna get my skills up in other mediums, hoping to combine it with my music. One day at a time. Much love.

Something wicked this way comes 🎵🎵 
April showers bring may flowers 🎶🎶
🙂😈
Someone up above must be looking out 4 me

NOISE POLLUTION OUT NOW
I’m excited to announce you can now listen to “Shaking”, the first single from my new album “Noise Pollution”
There‘s been a weight on my heart and Noise Pollution is how I’ve set it free. Consumed in darkness, I learned music has always illuminated my path forward. 
Allow me to guide you through the underworld.

My love and gratitude for music is at an all time high. I wake up everyday and I rejoice. I hear a song inside me.

I’m looking to take on some new projects/design work. The form is now open at www.Louie.Tech
I’m open to any sort of client/project, big or small. I’ve got over decade of experience making sounds, visuals, merch, and graphics. I’m here to help develop entity’s via 3D, audio, images, symbols, and video. Submit any type of project! Let’s see what comes my way!

Sugar Daddy OUT NOW

Happy pride from my husband and I. My new song sugar daddy is out today (go get that), a lot of the inspo came from my husband taking care of me when i needed it. It’s the last day of pride month and I had to give a shoutout, what a blessing it is to experience being loved by a trans dude. Okay happy pride, fuck the Supreme Court, go stream sugar daddy.
